Creating Measures.

Please copy and past this measures  one at time and follow gif steps  

1.   Total Success = SUM('Global Terrorism'[success])

 

 

2.   SUCCESS % = AVERAGE('Global Terrorism'[success])

 

3.   Success 10Yrs = CALCULATE([SUCCESS %],DATEADD('Date'[Date],-10,YEAR))

 

4.   DOD% = DIVIDE(([SUCCESS %]- [Success 10Yrs]),[Success 10Yrs])



Next step will be creating another measure for KPI it will help  us create red and green indicators  pleas follow gif steps  

.DOD =

SWITCH (

    TRUE (),

    [DOD%] < 0, UNICHAR ( 9660 ),

    UNICHAR ( 9650 )

)

    & ROUND ( [DOD%], 4 ) * 100 & " %"
